title: Barstool Pick Em 2017 Week Three
description:
EL Pres is BACK & betting everything under the sun. He and Big Cat break down all the big games of the weekend and also learn about the QBs of Notre Dames past. Our old friend Rico Bosco also calls in to finish off the show!!!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
